Name: Aixtron SE
Description: DELISTED - AIXTRON SE, together with its subsidiaries, provides deposition equipment to the semiconductor industry in worldwide. The company develops, produces, and installs deposition equipment for the deposition of semiconductor materials; provides process engineering, consulting, training, and ongoing customer support services; and offers peripheral equipment and services. Its technology solutions are used to build components for electronic and opto-electronic applications that are used in displays, signaling, lighting, fiber optic communication systems, wireless and mobile telephony applications, optical and electronic storage devices, computing, and other applications. The company markets and sells its products through its direct sales organization, dealers, and sales representatives. AIXTRON SE was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Herzogenrath, Germany.
